  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The effect of the expression `arr[i++] = i` is different depending on the evaluation order of the index `i++` and the right hand side `i`.  If the index is evaluated before the right hand side, an incremented value is assigned.\n\nThis issue keeps track of\n- [ ] making sure that the choice is documented\n- [ ] making sure that the choice is implemented\n",
